		<a name="breakfast" id="breakfast"></a>
		<h2>Breakfast in Bed</h2>
		<img src="images/Breakfast.jpg" alt="Breakfast in Bed"/>
		<!--- this image can be accessed at <a href="http://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/LocationPhotoDirectLink-g186338-d1153516-i80373835-The_Harrison_Gastro_Pub_and_Hotel-London_England.htmlhttp://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/LocationPhotoDirectLink-g186338-d1153516-i80373835-The_Harrison_Gastro_Pub_and_Hotel-London_England.html"--->
		<h3>Ingredients</h3>
		<ul>
		<li>2 eggs</li>
		<li>2 sausages</li>
		<li>2 slices of bacon</li>
		<li>2 hash browns</li>
		<li>2 tomatoes</li>
		<li>mushrooms</li>
		<li>2-4 slices of toast</li>
		<li>coffee or tea</li>
		<li>orange juice</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>Method</h3>
		<ul>
		<li>Heat up frying pan.</li>
		<li>Put oil in pan.</li>
		<li>Deep fry eggs.</li>
		<li>Deep fry sausauges.</li>
		<li>Deep fry slices of bacon.</li>
		<li>Deep fry hash browns.</li>
		<li>Serve up!! (add any extras you fancy e.g banana,apple,custard.. etc.)</li>
		</ul>
		
